      currently returns the raw stored value  ← still open, highest-priority security item
- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22 (migration 009): `auth.ts` login/totp SELECT/UPDATE of
      `display_name, theme, language, totp_secret_enc, totp_backup_codes` — added the columns
      (renamed plaintext `totp_secret`→`totp_secret_enc`). Also caught `pdf-receipts.ts`
      SELECTing `h.tagline` (same class of runtime crash) → added `hostels.tagline`.
      ⚠️ Migration 009 must be applied to any live DB.
- [x] PARTIAL 2026-07-22: role 'super_admin' (not in users CHECK) removed from the 6
      `requireRole` guards in students.ts — was a dead literal that never matched. NOTE: those
      GET/POST/PATCH student routes still exclude `chain_manager` while import/reveal-cnic
      include it — an authorization-policy inconsistency for the owner to decide (add
      chain_manager to student read/write? left unchanged).
